Steps for installation;

Step1:
----
sudo apt-get install libusb-1.0-0-dev 
git clone https://github.com/respeaker/mic_array_dfu.git
cd mic_array_dfu
make
sudo ./dfu --download respeaker_mic_array_8ch_raw.bin

Note:Refer the git link readme for additional details

Step 2:
-----
git clone https://github.com/respeaker/mic_array

